                           <script type="text/javascript">
                            var images = document.querySelectorAll('.g-tab-fader .g-photo-wrap'),
		counter = 0;

	setInterval(function(){
		var prev = counter

		counter++
		if(counter > images.length-1) counter = 0
		images[counter].classList.add('g-photo-active')
		// console.log(prev, counter)
		setTimeout(function(){
			// console.log(prev, counter)
			images[prev].classList.remove('g-photo-active')
		}, 250)
	}, 5000)
                           </script>

                      <script src="https://static01.nyt.com/video-static/vhs3/vhs.min.js">

                      <script>
                       ;(function() {

  // NYT app detection code
  var isInApp = !!(
    // sometimes this query param is present
    window.location.search.indexOf('nytapp') > -1 ||
    // usually the user agent is set
    window.navigator.userAgent.match(/nyt[-_]?(?:ios|android)/i) ||
    // on hybrid articles in android, the user agent and qs is missing
    (window.navigator.userAgent.match(/android/i) && window.__HYBRID__)
  );

  var isInAppHome = document.querySelector('.nytapp-home-interactive') !== null;
  var isAndroid = window.navigator.userAgent.indexOf('Android') > -1;
  var isIos = !!window.navigator.userAgent.match(/iP(hone|ad)/i);

  if (isInApp && isAndroid) document.querySelector('html').classList.add('nytapp-android');
  if (isInApp && isIos) document.querySelector('html').classList.add('nytapp-ios');

  // NYT apps resize function
  // Resizes the interactive webview height after a 1 second pause
  if ( window.NYTG && window.NYTG.enqueue) {
    setTimeout(function() {
      var container = document.querySelector("#g-hp-tabs");
      var windowWidth = window.innerWidth;
      function resize() {
        var height = container.offsetHeight;
        window.NYTG.enqueue(
          JSON.stringify({ id: 0, type: 'resize', options: { height: height } })
          )
      }
      window.addEventListener("resize", function() {
        if ( window.innerWidth != windowWidth ) {
          windowWidth = window.innerWidth;
          resize();
        }
      });
      resize();
    }, 1000);
  }


  var tabPromo = document.getElementById('g-hp-tabs')
  var tabs = tabPromo.querySelectorAll('.g-hp-tab')
  var buttons = tabPromo.querySelectorAll('.g-hp-tab-btn')

  for (var i = buttons.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
  	buttons[i].addEventListener('click', function(e){
  		for (var j = buttons.length - 1; j >= 0; j--) {
  			buttons[j].classList.remove('g-active')
  		}
  		var slug = this.getAttribute('data-tab')
  		this.classList.add('g-active')

  		for (var j = tabs.length - 1; j >= 0; j--) {
  			if(tabs[j].getAttribute('data-tab') === slug) {
  				tabs[j].classList.add('g-active')
  			} else {
  				tabs[j].classList.remove('g-active')
  			}
  		}
  		
  	}, false)
  }

  var video = tabPromo.querySelector('#g-vhs-video')

  if(video){

  		// console.log(video.offsetWidth)
	  	var wrap = video.querySelector('#g-vhs-video-wrap')
	  	

		const player = VHS.video({
			id: video.getAttribute('data-id'),
			container: wrap,
			headline: video.getAttribute('data-hed'),
			live: video.getAttribute('data-live'),
			autoplay: video.getAttribute('data-live'),
			muted: true,
			cover: false,
			ads: false,
			ratio: '16:9',
		    width: tabPromo.offsetWidth,
		    height: tabPromo.offsetWidth * 0.5625
		});

		if(isInAppHome || isAndroid || isIos){
			document.addEventListener('visibilitychange', function() {
			  if (document.visibilityState === "hidden") {
			    player.pause()
			  } else {
			  	player.play()
			  }
			})
		}
	}
/*
  var data_url = 'https://static01.nyt.com/newsgraphics/2020/03/09/hp-tabs/52f2883085464fab0829d554b462143d1c6fa65e/data.json'
  var data = {}, prev = data;

  var xhttp = new XMLHttpRequest();
  xhttp.onreadystatechange = function() {
    if (this.readyState == 4 && this.status == 200) {
    	const d = this.responseText

    	if(prev !== d){
    		data = JSON.parse( this.responseText )
			updateTabs()
    	}

    	prev = d
    }
  };
  xhttp.open("GET", data_url, true);
  xhttp.send();

  setInterval(function(){
  	xhttp.open("GET", data_url, true);
  	xhttp.send();
  }, 30000)

	function updateTabs(){
		// console.log(data)

		for (var i = data.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
			// tabs[i].setAttribute('data-tab', data[i].tab)
			if(data[i].is_active){
				tabs[i].classList.add('g-active')
			} else {
				tabs[i].classList.remove('g-active')
			}

			// var media = tabs[i].querySelector('.g-media-wrap')

			// 	media.querySelector('img').src = data[i].asset

			if(data[i].is_active){
				buttons[i].classList.add('g-active')
			} else {
				buttons[i].classList.remove('g-active')
			}
			// buttons[i].querySelector('button').innerText = data[i].button_text
		}
  	}
*/
})();

                  ;
(function() {

    // NYT app detection code
    var isInApp = !!(
        // sometimes this query param is present
        window.location.search.indexOf('nytapp') > -1 ||
        // usually the user agent is set
        window.navigator.userAgent.match(/nyt[-_]?(?:ios|android)/i) ||
        // on hybrid articles in android, the user agent and qs is missing
        (window.navigator.userAgent.match(/android/i) && window.__HYBRID__)
    );

    var isInAppHome = document.querySelector('.nytapp-home-interactive') !== null;
    var isAndroid = window.navigator.userAgent.indexOf('Android') > -1;
    var isIos = !!window.navigator.userAgent.match(/iP(hone|ad)/i);

    if (isInApp && isAndroid) document.querySelector('html').classList.add('nytapp-android');
    if (isInApp && isIos) document.querySelector('html').classList.add('nytapp-ios');

    // NYT apps resize function
    // Resizes the interactive webview height after a 1 second pause
    if (window.NYTG && window.NYTG.enqueue) {
        setTimeout(function() {
            var container = document.querySelector("#virus-service-nav");
            var windowWidth = window.innerWidth;

            function resize() {
                var height = container.offsetHeight;
                window.NYTG.enqueue(
                    JSON.stringify({ id: 0, type: 'resize', options: { height: height } })
                )
            }
            window.addEventListener("resize", function() {
                if (window.innerWidth != windowWidth) {
                    windowWidth = window.innerWidth;
                    resize();
                }
            });
            resize();
        }, 1000);
    }

})();

                       <p class="css-1pfq5u e1n8kpyg0">
                        Dozens of start-ups have laid off thousands, slashed costs and changed their businesses to try to survive the pandemic. All that may not work.
                       </p>
                      </a>
                      <div class="css-1slnf6i">
                       <div class="css-na047m">
                        <span class="css-ud8usf e1c8ga110">
                        </span>
                        <div class="css-16f7co2">
                        </div>
                       </div>
                      </div>
                     </div>
                    </div>
                   </article>

                 </div>

    if (window.INSTALL_RAVEN) {
  function installRaven() {
    /* eslint-disable */
// Install Raven
window.Raven
  .config('https://7bc8bccf5c254286a99b11c68f6bf4ce@sentry.io/178860', {
    release: vi.env.RELEASE,
    environment: vi.env.ENVIRONMENT,
    ignoreErrors: [/SecurityError: Blocked a frame with origin.*/],
  })
  .install();

// Stop using our error handler
window.nyt_errors.ravenInstalled = true;
var regex = /nyt-a=(.*?)(;|$)/;
var id = regex.exec(document.cookie);

if (id !== null) {
  id = id[1];
} else {
  id = '';
}

// Setting nyt-a as user context
window.Raven.setUserContext({
  id: id,
});

// Pass collected errors to Raven
var nytErrorsList = window.nyt_errors.list;
var nytErrorsTags = window.nyt_errors.tags;

for (var i = 0; i < nytErrorsList.length; i += 1) {
  var err = nytErrorsList[i];
  // weird?
  if (!err) { continue; }

  // also weird ... ?
  if (!err.err) {
    // maybe err itself is an Error?
    if (err instanceof Error) {
      window.Raven.captureException(err, err.data || {});
    } // else { silently ignore? }
  }

  // just making sure ...
  if (err.err instanceof Error) {
    window.Raven.captureException(err.err, err.data || {});
  } // else { silently ignore? }
}

// Pass collected Tags to Raven
for (var i = 0; i < nytErrorsTags.length; i += 1) {
  window.Raven.setTagsContext(nytErrorsTags[i]);
}

  }
  window.addEventListener('load', function(event) {
    if (!window.Raven) {
      var includeRaven = document.getElementById("RavenInstaller");
      var script = document.createElement("script");
      script.src = "/vi-assets/static-assets/raven.min-830a6d04a55c283934dd1893d6ddc66d.js";
      script.onload = function() {
        installRaven();
      };
      includeRaven.appendChild(script);
    } else {
      installRaven();
    }
  });
}
